{"tid":1324743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府回應遊行","createTime":"2019-07-16T15:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T09:48:47.000Z","uid":62032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c5862c1c090644503f430169b0a2661623385c32","tid":1324743,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"Sorry Old News<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知大家呢幾日好嬲警察同新城市垃圾<br />\n但係我好想提返大家<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好畀人分散注意力</span></span><br />\n唔好忘記點解<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">612</span></span>咁多人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">走上街頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今年6月9日 23:07&rdquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府回應</span></span>遊行&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n...今日參加遊行的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人數雖然很多</span></span>...《條例草案》將於六月十二日在<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">立法會恢復二讀</span></span>辯論...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/09/P2019060900579.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201906%2F09%2FP2019060900579.htm&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2Bc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=e7206785\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/09/P2019060900579.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n班<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">高官分明想分散注意力</span></span></span><br />\n令大家集中喺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">警民對立</span></span><br />\n佢哋就喺屋企涼冷氣開開心心<br />\n警察同示威者就喺街熱到死互相仇視<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最終得益嘅會係邊個？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n謹記<br />\n&ldquo;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">別讓林鄭月娥跑了</span></span>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&md